additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Vapour may be harmful. May give off dangerous gas if mixed with other products. Irritant. Wash hands after use. Read safety directions. If swallowed, do not induce vomiting. Remove as much product as possible form the mouth. Rinse mouth with water and seek medical attention.If in eyes: hold eyelids apart and flush the eye continuously with running water. Continue flushing until advised to stop by a Poisons Information Centre or a doctor, or for at least 15 minutes.For medical advice call: Contact a Poison Information Centre on 13 11 26 (Australia) 0800 764 766 (NZ) or a doctor (at once).
